listDescription:
I meticulously evaluated all applications within the Collective Gov category, assessing their impact based on my experience. I've acknowledged and commended each application that successfully passed the initial review, with the exception of one where I felt profit exceeded impact. 
To clarify the rationale behind my allocation, I've aimed for a balanced and pragmatic distribution—a conservative yet realistic approach.
impactEvaluationDescription:
To assess the impact of each application within the Collective Gov category, I employed a comprehensive method utilizing a Google Sheet (referenced below). Initially, I conducted a personal evaluation, assigning an impact score out of 100 to each application. This evaluation was based on various factors and ultimately came down to my personal experiences 

I proceeded to conduct an independent analysis, specifically evaluating the gap between profit and the impact of every application, enabling me to make informed decisions. My target allocation strategy involved rounding off the allocation amounts to the nearest 5,000 OP, ensuring a structured and practical distribution. To maintain objectivity, I deliberately removed my personal comments on each application within the sheet,
